## Hints for Future Agents
- --game-ink flips to cream (#fff7d6) in dark mode, so it CANNOT be used as foreground for light surfaces like --game-cyan. Use a literal #1e1b4d for the foreground of any surface that stays light in both themes.
- sidebar-accent-foreground and other sidebar-* tokens still reference var(--game-ink) in .dark — if sidebar cyan surfaces ever appear, they'll have the same bug. Out of scope for this task but worth noting.
- The three bg-accent consumers touched here were the only ones without text-accent-foreground. Other consumers (game-client.tsx:1353, :3028, round-highlights-carousel.tsx:194) already had it.

